Tekne has taken part to the ‘Settimana Pedagogica’ (Pedagogical week) sponsored by the Order of Engineers of Chieti, hosted by the Institute of Higher Education ‘Algeri Marino’ of Casoli (Chieti province, Italy). Among numerous speeches, Tekne took an active part in the seminar entitled ‘The 5G Network: what is it and how will our everyday life change’, which saw the participation of university professors and industry representatives to showthe peculiar characteristics of the new technology and the new R&T projects connected to it. Tekne, represented by our eng. Veneziano Palmerio, head of the Electronics & Systems business unit, highlighted the possible application effects in the short and medium term on which Tekne is focused.